@Sergey-Lyapin When cookie notice is hidden then content is not clickable (maybe it depends on location, I don't know).
I have updated it - https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/commit/9499ccff7487bf4ccdc1a84046bb7478cdf7a2de
For this kind of cookie notice, please next time add domain to this rule - `||cmp.inmobi.com^$domain=[...]`

Also missing:
```
euronews.com###o-site-hr__leaderboard-wallpaper.u-show-for-xlarge {remove:true;}
read.amazon.*###readerChromeOverlayBottom.readerChromeOverlayBottom-banner-desktop {bottom: 0 !important;}
twitch.tv##.video-player--stream-display-ad_lower-third {height: 100% !important;}
dailystar.co.uk##[data-testid="commercial-above-header-box-1"] {remove:true;}
```
